(e) a  party's  place  of  business  is  presumed  to  be  the  location indicated  by  that  party,  unless  another  party  demonstrates  that the party making the indication does not have a place of business  at that location; and

(f) 'usual place of residence' in relation to a body corporate,  means the place where it is registered.

